org.openntf.domino.nsfdata.structs.cd

Class CDBORDERINFO

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openntf.domino.nsfdata.structs.AbstractStruct
      • org.openntf.domino.nsfdata.structs.cd.CDRecord
        • org.openntf.domino.nsfdata.structs.cd.CDBORDERINFO
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Externalizable, java.io.Serializable

    public class CDBORDERINFO
extends CDRecord
    This CD record describes border information for a given table. This CD record will be preceded with CD record CDPRETABLEBEGIN both encapsulated between a CDBEGINRECORD and a CDENDRECORD record with CD record signature CDPRETABLEBEGIN. (editods.h)
    Since:
    Lotus Notes/Domino 5.0
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
